00208 void FusionCELDataGCOSTest::CompareHeaderData()
00209 {
00210         // Check all header values
00211         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetVersion() == gcosCel->GetVersion());
00212         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCols() == gcosCel->GetCols());
00213         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetRows() == gcosCel->GetRows());
00214         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumCells() == gcosCel->GetNumCells());
00215 
00216         std::string headerString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetHeader());
00217         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(headerString == gcosCel->GetHeaderString());
00218         std::string algString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlg());
00219         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(algString == gcosCel->GetAlg());
00220         std::string paramString = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetParams());
00221         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(paramString == gcosCel->GetParams());
00222         std::string chipTypetring = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetChipType());
00223         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chipTypetring == gcosCel->GetChipType());
00224 
00225         std::string params = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetParams());
00226         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel->GetParams() == params);
00227         std::string algorithmParameters = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameters());
00228         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameters() == algorithmParameters);
00229         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters() == gcosCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters());
00230         int paramCount = fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00231         for (int ip = 0; ip < paramCount; ++ip)
00232         {
00233                 std::wstring fusionParamTag = fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00234                 std::string gcosParamTag = gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00235                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionParamTag) == gcosParamTag);
00236                 std::string fusionParamValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(fusionParamTag.c_str()));
00237                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionParamValue == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(gcosParamTag.c_str()));
00238         }
00239 
00240         // Test GetParameters
00241         FusionTagValuePairTypeList& calvinList = fusionCel->GetParameters();
00242         int gcosParamCount = gcosCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00243 
00244         std::list<FusionTagValuePairType>::iterator ci = calvinList.begin();
00245 
00246         for (int gi = 0; ci != calvinList.end() && gi < gcosParamCount; ++ci, ++gi)
00247         {
00248                 std::string calvinTag = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(ci->Tag);
00249                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinTag == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(gi));
00250                 std::string calvinValue = StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(ci->Value);
00251                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinValue == gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(gcosCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(gi).c_str()));
00252                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->Tag == ci->DetailedType().GetName());
00253                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->Value == ci->DetailedType().GetValueText());
00254         }
00255 
00256         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCellMargin() == gcosCel->GetCellMargin());
00257         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumOutliers() == gcosCel->GetNumOutliers());
00258         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumMasked() == gcosCel->GetNumMasked());
00259         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(StringUtils::ConvertWCSToMBS(fusionCel->GetDatHeader()) == gcosCel->GetDatHeader());
00260         
00261         CompareGridCoordinates();
00262 }

00264 void FusionCELDataGCOSTest::CompareGridCoordinates()
00265 {
00266         // Check the grid
00267         affymetrix_fusion_io::FGridCoords fusionGrid = fusionCel->GetGridCorners();
00268         GridCoordinatesType gcosRect = gcosCel->GetGridCorners();
00269         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperleft.x = (float)gcosRect.upperleft.x);
00270         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperleft.y = (float)gcosRect.upperleft.y);
00271         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperright.x = (float)gcosRect.upperright.x);
00272         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.upperright.y = (float)gcosRect.upperright.y);
00273         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerright.x = (float)gcosRect.lowerright.x);
00274         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerright.y = (float)gcosRect.lowerright.y);
00275         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerleft.x = (float)gcosRect.lowerleft.x);
00276         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionGrid.lowerleft.y = (float)gcosRect.lowerleft.y);
00277 }

00566 void FusionCELDataGCOSTest::ClearTest()
00567 {
00568         fusionCel->SetFileName(GCOS_CEL_FILE.c_str());
00569         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->Read() == true);
00570         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(fusionCel->Clear());
00571 
00572         gcosCel->SetFileName(GCOS_CEL_FILE.c_str());
